-pf-type="Paragraph3">9. Reward Loyal Customers</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-92_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-93_"><p class="sc-jUosCB eIJFN pf-94_ pf-gs-paragraph-1" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">If you're struggling, your customers are too. Reward them for being loyal in a difficult time. Offer coupons and discounts. This is an easy thing to do with social media. Offer promotions for sharing your posts or tagging you. Give your customers a reason to be loyal and they will be. If you want to learn more about cultivating customer loyalty, read this article.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-96_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0268/4508/5731/files/Person_Holding_Credit_Card.jpg?v=1614289976" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0268/4508/5731/files/Person_Holding_Credit_Card.jpg?v=1614289976 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0268/4508/5731/files/Person_Holding_Credit_Card_500x.jpg?v=1614289976 320w" width="2309" height="1732" alt="person paying with credit card" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-97_"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-98_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-99_"><p class="sc-jUosCB eIJFN pf-100_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10. Be Open About Your Precautions</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-102_ pf-